CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 15, 1970, pg. 22 reads: "These Young Lovelies were fashionably mod as they "did their thing" in "Soul Dressings '70" Fashion show. First photo, from left to right: Wrenna Watson, Lidya Fulton, Stephanie Yee and Won'que King...-Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Wrenna Watson, Lidya Fulton, Stephanie Yee and Won'que King, modeling clothing during the "Soul Dressings '70" fashion show
